  "text": "AM sensors consist of a three-axis MEMS accelerometer and three-axis magnetometer. The accelerometer gives the specific force measurement of a rigid body, and the magnetometer provides the users with the sensed local Earth geomagnetic field according to the IGRFmodel [CITATION_1] .",
